t: "Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe, wata on waru mbaroodi=raddaande hara ko on horminii …ìe. Kala war…óo ndi e moo…óon ko o tewii…óo, njo…ìdi mun, ko yeru kon ko o wari neemoraa…ói, √±aawa …óum joomiraa…ìe nun…óal …ói…óo e moo…óon, neldaari yottotoondi Kaaba on, maa kaffaara √±ammingol miskiim…ìe, maa ko fotata …óum …óon koorka fii yo o mee…óu battane fiyaake makko on. Alla Yaafike kon ko fe∆¥∆¥i ; kala ruttii…óo, Alla Yottoto e Makko. Alla ko Foolu…óo, Jom-yottagol"